				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Getting the Neriad Shawl<a name="22296"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 18 04 7:39 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Wouldn't use charm for the mermaids, but if you want to clear some of the outer area, it helps kill elementals.  The mermaids who drop the shawl are pretty mean relative to their level.  With &quot;decent gear&quot; you'll most likely have to stop to regen some... I remember the melee mermaids hitting nearly 300 max and being rogues.
<br />
 
<br />
What was a bit troublesome at first was getting to the castle area safely... there are often see invis fish in the way, so fade/DA will probably be useful.  Not entirely sure about what sees invis down there now that it's revamped, but keep your eye out. In general, there's nothing too outragous about this camp if you scout it out and play it safe.
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
