				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Getting the Neriad Shawl<a name="24473"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 28 04 7:31 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Well me and a friend moved to SG when we were both about lvl 65//60 and 65//100. Both about 4000hp and decent gear.
<br />
Meleed//Mezzed//Dawnsonged em. If one of us went low, he dawned -.-.
<br />

<br />
All except the SeaPrincess (Those drop em) wont move on landside, so you can use Fading Memories oder Camp if you got agro.
<br />
Princesses will move on land side.
<br />

<br />
We moved with DA and Fading Memories to em.
<br />
Zone in, DA up, right hand till end, into a cave and theres a Landside in it. On the landside there spawns a Bullwarg some metres away. Wont agro if you stay away. There you can FM and med up.
<br />

<br />
Marrs+Nivs did good hp regen for us. Melee did the rest.
<br />

<br />

<br />
Took about 10hours of camping for two Shawls ;)
<br />

<br />
Good Luck =)</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
